  19 Jun 2008; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org>
  ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r3.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #227679

  19 Jun 2008; Olivier Crête <tester@gentoo.org>
  ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r3.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64, bug #227679

  06 Apr 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r2.ebuild, ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r3.ebuild:
  Add missing pkgconfig dependency, fixing #216381

  06 Apr 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r2.ebuild, ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r3.ebuild:
  This version of ruby-glib2 does not work with ruby 1.9. Thanks for 
  Tarmo Tänav in #216367 for the suggested fix.

  28 Mar 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -ruby-glib2-0.14.1.ebuild,
  -ruby-glib2-0.15.0.ebuild, -ruby-glib2-0.16.0.ebuild,
  -ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old versions

*ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r3 (28 Mar 2008)

  28 Mar 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  +files/ruby-glib2-0.16.0-glib-2.16.patch, +ruby-glib2-0.16.0-r3.ebuild:
  Add patch from upstream to allow compilation with glib 2.16. Closes #213393.
  Thank for leio for already providing the patch.

